  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1316666">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1316666/" class="title-link">尤米尼斯传奇</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1316666"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Pai/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1040722-26.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Pai/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">VIVI DURGA</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-02"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-02 09:23:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1316666_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我总是能在恰当的时间看到适合的作品，《历史之眼》就又是一个如此的例子。  初次看到封面的时候，片面地认为是恐怖漫画或是奇幻类的，但实际上却是历史题材的漫画。  随着尤米尼斯的旅程，领略到了欧陆古典时期的风土人情以及当时的社会变迁——并且书中提到了一个与主角休戚...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1316666/#comments">(30回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1316666_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1316666_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2437094">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2437094/" class="title-link">《历史之眼》中出现的历史人物</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2437094"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fire_and_ocean/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4148045-274.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fire_and_ocean/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">朔风</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-01"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-01 08:25:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2437094_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  台湾人的译名太怪异了...  梅牧诺：可以肯定是罗德斯岛的梅农。样子有些枭雄，很明显是冷静派，符合历史。日本漫画一大定律是必须要有一个冷酷的冰山男形象，估计就是梅农了。梅农出生于公元前380年，比亚历山大要年长24岁，漫画里的梅农却是青年形象，这一点很明显是虚构。  ...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2437094/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2437094_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2437094_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1487508">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1487508/" class="title-link">怎么样的笔画，讲述着怎么样的一个传奇？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1487508"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1956257/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1956257-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1956257/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">amelie</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-09-03"
      class="main-meta">2008-09-03 10:47:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1487508_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  低智商、肥皂剧呕像剧爱好者人勿看！ 原本的《寄生兽》我就很喜欢《七夕之国》有那么一点轻巧，尤其是结尾部分，《神鬼战略》是神作， 我本来就喜欢古希腊罗马马其顿历史～～可惜我才看到4，岩明大人，我能活着看到完结么？你可不要学永野护呀！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1487508/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
