  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2508905">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2508905/" class="title-link">一个神的故事</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2508905"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1562652/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1562652-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1562652/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">做梦的猫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-12"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-12 17:54:59</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2508905_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  所谓的神并不是指书的主角，而是岩明均本人。 出神作的作者在漫画史上并不少，但是出了一本又一本神作的人绝对属于凤毛麟角，对于这样的作者我们可以称之为神人。  他对于作品的节奏把握，实在是令人叹服到五体投地。 他的每一本书都好像自然界鬼斧神工一般，恰到好处，绝不拖...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2508905/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2508905_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2508905_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2091868">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2091868/" class="title-link">其实我是推荐另外本历史漫画，海盗战记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2091868"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mjay1984/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mjay1984/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-24"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-24 21:05:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2091868_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  同样50话，幸村城的效率是高出不少，故事也已经进入高潮王位争夺战，而历史之言才刚刚来开序幕（亚历山大争夺王位感觉太没悬念了），也不知道作者打算连载多久。。。怨念，虽然2本我都很喜欢，不过个人认为幸村城的画风更占些便宜，比较像三浦的烙印，现在到第七卷，没看过的去...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2091868/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
